      "content": "people saying \"it gets better\" or \"reach out\" just feels like they aren't listening. it doesn't get better. the person who made my life make sense is just... gone. it's like the sun went out and everyone's just telling me to find a flashlight. i don't want a flashlight. i just want the dark to stop feeling so heavy. it feels like there's nothing left of me to actually help.",
